INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("14", "1", "2014-03-16 08:26:06", "2014-03-16 08:26:06", "<b>Baby sleeping bags designed by Sweet Baby Lilly stand for safety, quality and style. We believe in providing only<em> the best baby sleeping bags</em> for you and your baby.</b>\r\n\r\nOur range of <em>European </em>designed, <em>stylish</em> and <em>brightly coloured</em> baby sleeping bags have been specifically designed to provide a safe and healthy sleeping environment for your baby. Your baby or toddler might be alone in their baby sleeping bag for up to 12 hours at night so it needs to be as safe as possible. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your peace of mind is our priority</span>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Baby sleeping bag safety features</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Certified to the highest children’s sleeping product <strong>safety standards: Australian</strong> AS/NZS 1249:2003, and <strong>American</strong> CPSIA.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>100% breathable cotton</strong> for ventilation to prevent overheating.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Protective</strong> cotton layer around <strong>zipper</strong> to protect baby’s skin against zipper teeth.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Closed </strong>and<strong> non-metal zipper pull </strong>to protect baby\'s teeth when pulling up their legs and suck on the zipper</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Provides a stable sleeping environment for baby by supporting a <strong>consistent body temperature</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Non restrictive, unique bell-curved shape to <strong>stimulate baby’s hip development</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe take pride in using only the <em>finest quality</em> cotton and<em> lead-free</em> materials, while maintaining strict quality control around fabric selection and product manufacturing to meet the quality demands of safety conscious mums.\r\n\r\n<strong>Additional baby sleeping bag features</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-stretch premium cotton to avoid stretching of neck holes and stepping out of the bag.</li>\r\n	<li>Oversized and reversed zippers for <strong>easy nappy changes.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Super soft and seamless cotton inner lining for baby’s<strong> comfort.</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Size specific and <strong>fitted neck hole</strong> to avoid slipping into the baby sleeping bag.</li>\r\n	<li>Size specific and <strong>fitted arm hole</strong> for ventilation to prevent overheating.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Front zipper</strong> to remember the parent to put the baby on the back to sleep safety.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAll these features will make Sweet Baby Lilly wearable baby sleeping bags <em>safe</em>, <em>cosy</em> and <em>easy to use</em>. Sweet Baby Lilly baby sleeping bags will help your baby sleep tight, so you both enjoy a well deserved rest, every night.\r\n\r\n<b>Sweet dreams!</b>\r\n\r\n<strong><b>Juliette (founder, Sweet Baby Lilly).</b></strong>", "Home", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "home", "", "", "2015-05-07 13:13:27", "2015-05-07 13:13:27", "", "0", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/?page_id=14", "0", "page", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("15", "1", "2014-03-16 08:26:06", "2014-03-16 08:26:06", "", "Home", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "14-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-03-16 08:26:06", "2014-03-16 08:26:06", "", "14", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/14-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("16", "1", "2014-03-16 08:27:10", "2014-03-16 08:27:10", "<strong>Safe Sleep tips for mums and dads to ensure a healthy and safe baby sleep for your little one</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Place your baby on his or her back when putting to sleep.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure baby’s face and head is and stays uncovered.</li>\r\n	<li>Do not let your baby become overheated. Monitor your baby’s temperature. Use light clothing and keep the room temperature at a comfortable level (65˚F or 18˚C).</li>\r\n	<li>Use a one-piece sleeper or a baby sleeping bag, instead of blankets.</li>\r\n	<li>Use only a cot that meets current Australian safety standards</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure baby’s mattress is firm, clean, flat, and the correct size for the cot.</li>\r\n	<li>Only cover the mattress with a tight fitting sheet.</li>\r\n	<li>Never place your baby to sleep on any soft surface.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure that the cot is free from toys, pillows, etc. Nothing should be in, attached to, or draped over the side of the cot.</li>\r\n	<li>Place your baby to sleep in his or her own sleep area, instead of bed sharing.</li>\r\n	<li>Do not use wedges or positioning devices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor more Safe Sleep advise for your baby, please read the SIDS &amp; Kids Safe Sleeping <a href=\"http://www.sidsandkids.org/safe-sleeping/\">recommendations</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;", "Safe Sleep", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "safe-baby-sleep", "", "", "2015-05-17 07:17:07", "2015-05-17 07:17:07", "", "0", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/?page_id=16", "0", "page", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("17", "1", "2014-03-16 08:27:10", "2014-03-16 08:27:10", "", "Healthy Sleep", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "16-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-03-16 08:27:10", "2014-03-16 08:27:10", "", "16", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/16-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("18", "1", "2014-03-16 08:27:45", "2014-03-16 08:27:45", "<a href=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1.png\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-135\" alt=\"OurStory1\" src=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1-253x300.png\" width=\"253\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly, an international brand of safe, premium quality and stylish baby sleeping bags, was founded by Juliette Tanamal after she gave birth to her beautiful daughter, Lilly-Ann in 2012.\r\n\r\nAs most new Mums do, Juliette extensively researched the different options of all things baby – including baby bedding and sleeping materials. The research she encountered indicate that baby sleeping bags provide a safer and healthier alternative to loose sheets and blankets. After trialing for herself, she also found that her precious Lilly-Ann improved her sleep patterns with the use of baby sleeping bags.\r\n\r\nAs a result, Juliette became an advocate for baby sleeping bags, however found it a struggle to find sleeping bags that were not only safe, but also of high quality and fashionable enough to suit her as a young new mum. The ones she did find were either overpriced, poorly made, didn’t meet safety standards or just simply too plain in design.\r\n\r\nIt was at this time that Juliette decided to make it her mission to create a range of baby sleeping products that were not only cute and stylish, but also met the highest quality and safety standards. Hence, Sweet Baby Lilly was born, giving parents peace of mind and mums and babies a well deserved rest.", "Our Story", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "our-story", "", "", "2015-05-12 23:23:49", "2015-05-12 23:23:49", "", "0", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/?page_id=18", "0", "page", "", "0");
