INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("136", "1", "2015-05-11 12:46:30", "2015-05-11 12:46:30", "<a href=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1.png\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-135\" alt=\"OurStory1\" src=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1-253x300.png\" width=\"253\" height=\"300\" /></a>\n\nSweet Baby Lilly, an international brand of safe, premium quality and stylish baby sleeping bags, was founded by Juliette Tanamal after she gave birth to her beautiful daughter, Lilly-Ann in 2012.\n\nAs most new Mums do, Juliette extensively researched the different options of all things baby – including baby bedding and sleeping materials. The research she encountered indicate that baby sleeping bags provide a safer and healthier alternative to loose sheets and blankets. After trialing for herself, she also found that her precious Lilly-Ann improved her sleep patterns with the use of baby sleeping bags.\n\nAs a result, Juliette became an advocate for baby sleeping bags, however found it a struggle to find sleeping bags that were not only safe, but also of high quality and fashionable enough to suit her as a young new mum. The ones she did find were either overpriced, poorly made, didn’t meet safety standards or just simply too plain in design.\n\nIt was at this time that Juliette decided to make it her mission to create a range of baby sleeping products that were not only cute and stylish, but also met the highest quality and safety standards. Hence, Sweet Baby Lilly was born, giving parents peace of mind and mums and babies a well deserved rest.", "Our Story", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "18-autosave-v1", "", "", "2015-05-11 12:46:30", "2015-05-11 12:46:30", "", "18", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/18-autosave-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("137", "1", "2014-04-30 05:16:45", "2014-04-30 05:16:45", "<a href=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-135\" alt=\"OurStory1\" src=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1-253x300.png\" width=\"253\" height=\"300\" /></a>Sweet Baby Lilly, an international brand of safe, premium quality and stylish baby sleeping products, was founded by Juliette Tanamal in 2012, 1 year after she gave birth to her sweet baby girl, Lilly-Ann.\r\n\r\nAfter travelling the globe for more than a decade, and living in Europe, Australia and the US, Juliette was amazed to find that many parents were still using loose blankets to keep their babies snug.\r\n\r\nThis came as a surprise to Juliette, as extensive research indicates that baby sleeping bags, also know as wearable baby blankets, provide a safer and healthier alternative, preventing the risks often associated with loose blankets.\r\n\r\nJuliette found it a struggle to find baby sleeping bags that were not only safe, but also of high quality and more fashionable. The ones she found were either overpriced, poorly made or simply too plain!\r\n\r\nJuliette decided to made it her mission to create a range of baby sleeping products that were not only cute and hip, but also met the highest quality and safety standards, giving parents piece of mind and mums and babies a well deserved rest.", "Our Story", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "18-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-04-30 05:16:45", "2014-04-30 05:16:45", "", "18", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/18-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
