INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("143", "1", "2014-04-30 05:21:59", "2014-04-30 05:21:59", "<div style=\"margin: 20px 70px 20px 70px;\">\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/iStock_000023242971_Medium.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-142\" alt=\"iStock_000023242971_Medium\" src=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/iStock_000023242971_Medium-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /></a>Shop</h1>\r\nJuliette found it a struggle to find baby sleeping bags that were not only safe, but also of high quality and more fashionable. The ones she found were either overpriced, poorly made or simply too plain!\r\n\r\nJuliette decided to made it her mission to create a range of baby sleeping products that were not only cute and hip, but also met the highest quality and safety standards, giving parents piece of mind and mums and babies a well deserved rest.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Certified to the highest children’s sleeping product safety standards: the Australian AS-NZS: 1249.2003 and American CPSIA.</li>\r\n	<li>100% super soft cotton to prevent overheating.</li>\r\n	<li>Assist in SIDS (Sudden Infant Death Syndrome) prevention.</li>\r\n	<li>Eliminate the risk of suffocation and variation in body temperature often associated with loose blankets.</li>\r\n	<li>Protective layer around zipper stop and teeth to protect baby’s skin.</li>\r\n	<li>Non-metal and closed zipper pull tab to protect baby’s teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>Unique bell-curved shape to stimulate hip movement.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe take pride in using only the finest quality cotton and lead-free materials, and maintaining strict quality control around fabric selection and stitching to meet the quality demands of safety conscious mums\r\n\r\nAdditional features, such as oversized and reversed zippers for easy nappy changes, seamless linings for comfort, and 2 breathable cotton layers for ventilation, make the Sweet Baby Lilly wearable baby blankets not only safe, but also very snug and easy to use.\r\n\r\nCute, cosy, warm and comfortable, the Sweet Baby Lilly wearable baby  blankets will help your baby to sleep tight, so you can both enjoy a well deserved rest, every night.\r\n\r\nSweet dreams!\r\n\r\nJuliette (founder, Sweet Baby Lilly).\r\n\r\n</div>", "Shop", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "7-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-04-30 05:21:59", "2014-04-30 05:21:59", "", "7", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/7-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
