other use of your information. In addition, when we partner with another company to offer or provide products, services, contests or promotions, we may compare our customer list with theirs to identify common customers to avoid any redundant communication or Service, and to fulfil our promotional obligations. <b> </b>\r\n\r\nWhen we offer contests, sweepstakes and promotions, with or without a marketing partner, you may be required to provide certain Personal Information in order to participate. In these cases, we will give you the choice not to receive email messages or other communications from us regarding our products, services, contests, and promotions. In this case, however, we may still need to contact you, for example, to notify winners or to fulfil our promotional obligations.\r\n\r\nIn the unlikely event of a sale of some or all of our business, we will disclose your Personal Information to a purchaser that agrees to abide by the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.\r\n\r\nWe also reserve the right to disclose information about you as required by law, in response to a legal process or law enforcement requests, and as necessary to protect the property, interests and rights of our company, our affiliates, and others partners.\r\n\r\n<b>Use of forums</b>\r\n\r\nIn the event we make message boards, forums or blogs available to you (collectively, \"Forums\"), you will be solely responsible for the information and any other content you post on and through these Forums. You should be aware that when you voluntarily disclose personal information on or through these Forums, such information is generally accessible to, and may be collected and used by, other users. This may result in unsolicited messages from third parties, because these messages are beyond our control. We do not exercise control over any users or Site visitors, and in no way are we responsible, nor do we have any liability whatsoever, for any collection or use of information you may disclose through the Forums. Our Privacy Policy does not cover such disclosure of information. We encourage you to exercise discretion when providing personal information about yourself in and through Forums. Please do not post any personal information via a Forum that you expect to keep private.\r\n\r\n<b>Use of cookies and automatically collected data</b>\r\n\r\nIf you have permitted your computer to accept cookies, we may use cookies on our Site. Cookies are pieces of information that our Site transfers to your computer’s hard drive to make your web-surfing and website navigation easier by saving personal preferences and browsing patterns while you are at our Site.\r\n\r\nCookies may be used to analyse our Site usage and behaviour, or to relate your use of our Site to other information about you, including your Personal Information. All of these purposes only serve to improve, customize or personalize our Site content or design or to improve your shopping experience with us. Most web browsers, like Internet Explorer, can be set to inform you when a cookie has been sent to you and provide you with the opportunity to refuse that cookie. However, refusing a cookie may in some cases preclude you from using our Site, negatively impact the display or function of our Site, or certain areas or features of our Site.\r\n\r\nOur servers may automatically collect data about your Internet address when you visit our Site. This information, known as an Internet Protocol address, or IP Address, is a number that is automatically assigned to your computer by your Internet Service Provider whenever you are on the Internet. When you request pages from our Site, our servers may log your IP Address to help us identify you and to gather demographic information, such as your country of origin, to connect you to the right Site. It does not include personally identifiable information. Our server may also record the pages you visit on our Site, the ads you see and/or click on via our Site, or other information like search terms you have entered on our Site. We use this data for internal Site administration and to help diagnose problems with our Site. We will not link any Personal Information to this automatically collected data of our users.<b></b>\r\n\r\n<b>Third party sites</b><b></b>\r\n\r\nYou may arrive at our Site via another website. In addition, our Site may contain links that will let you leave our Site and access another website. We provide these links solely for the convenience and information of our visitors. Websites that are linked to or from our Site are not under our control and it is possible that these websites have a different privacy policy. We urge you to review those policies before providing any personal information as we accept no responsibility or liability for these other websites. Our Privacy Policy applies solely to information that is acquired on our Site or through your use of our Service, and/or your relationship with us.\r\n\r\n<b>Managing and accessing your personal information</b>\r\n\r\nWe will take reasonable steps to keep your Personal Information accurate and up-to-date.  If you provided your email address to us and wish to update it, you may do so by updating your account information on our Site, or by sending an email to <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com\">info@sweetbabylilly.com</a>.au.  Please be sure to include your full name and the email or physical address you used when you registered with us or made a purchase from us.\r\n\r\nIf you no longer wish to receive email or promotional communication from us or our affiliates, such as offers, updates and newsletters, you may opt-out of receiving such communications by following the instructions included in each communication.  In addition, you can remove your email address from promotional lists at any time by sending an email with the subject line of UNSUBSCRIBE to <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com\">info@sweetbabylilly.com</a>.au. Please be sure to include your full name, email and physical address you used when you registered with us or made a purchase from us.\r\n\r\nIf you wish to delete your account with us, you can send us an email with the subject line of DEACTIVATE to <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com.au\">info@sweetbabylilly.com.au</a>. Please be sure to include your full name, email and physical address you used when you registered with us or made a purchase from us.\r\n\r\nAt your request, we will provide you with a copy of any Personal Information we hold about you, unless an exception to the <i>Privacy Act 1988</i> (Cth) applies.  Please send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com.au\">info@sweetbabylilly.com.au</a> if you would like to obtain a record of any Personal Information we hold about you.\r\n\r\n<b>Protecting Children’s Privacy</b>\r\n\r\nWe are very serious about the safety of children when they use the Internet. Our Site is not intended for or designed to attract anyone under the age of 13. Consistent with and in the spirit of the Children\'s Online Privacy Protection Act  1998 (USA), we will never intentionally or knowingly request or collect personal information on our Site from anyone under the age of 13 (or older in some jurisdictions) without prior verifiable parental consent. We encourage parents to be involved in the online activities of their children to ensure that no information is collected from a child without parental permission. If we receive actual knowledge that someone under the age of 13 is providing information on our Site, or that someone is providing information about a person under the age of 13 on our Site, we will remove all personally identifiable information about that person from our files.\r\n\r\n<b>How to make a complaint</b>\r\n\r\nIf you wish to make a complaint about the collection, use or disclosure of your Personal Information pursuant to this Privacy Policy, please contact the Privacy Officer, PO Box 64, Rozelle NSW 2039 or by email on <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com.au\">info@sweetbabylilly.com.au</a>.\r\n\r\nComplaints will be forwarded to the Privacy Officer who will acknowledge your complaint within 7 days of receipt of your complaint in writing.  Our Privacy Officer will investigate your complaint and respond to you with our decision within 30 days of receiving your complaint in writing.  If you do not agree with our response, you can request a review or request resolution through a recognised external dispute resolution scheme.  Alternatively, you can contact the Commissioner of the Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC) at www.oaic.gov.au.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Revision Date: 29-5-14</span>", "Privacy Policy", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "118-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-06-06 05:03:18", "2014-06-06 05:03:18", "", "118", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/index.php/118-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("179", "1", "2014-06-06 05:05:23", "2014-06-06 05:05:23", "This Delivery &amp; Return Policy should be read in conjunction with our Terms and Conditions of Use.\r\n\r\n<b>Delivery</b>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Process</span></b>\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly products ordered via www.sweetbabylilly.com.au can only be delivered within Australia via Australia Post. At the moment, Sweet Baby Lilly in Australia is not able to process any international orders.\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly will dispatch your order within 2 business days from the date of receiving your order, however goods can only be dispatched once payment is cleared. Risk in the goods passes to you when it leaves our warehouse.  Sweet Baby Lilly cannot be held responsible for any undelivered items by Australia Post.\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Time</span></b>\r\n\r\nFor an estimated shipping time of your goods after dispatch (subject always to Australia Post turnaround times), please see the table below:\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>                  Destination</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Major Cities</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\"><b>Regional</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>New South Wales</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">1-2 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">2-4 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Victoria                     </b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">2-3 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">3-5 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Queensland            </b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">2-3 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">3-5 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>South Australia      </b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">3-4 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">4-6 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Tasmania</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">5-6 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">6-8 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Western Australia</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">5-6 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">6-8 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Northern Territory</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">5-6 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">6-10 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\"><b>Australian Capital Territory</b></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"150\">2-3 Days</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"118\">3-5 Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Payment</span></b>\r\n\r\nShipping is FREE for all standard sized orders (maximum of 2kg) around Australia with a total order value of $130 or more. Sweet Baby Lilly charges a low flat fee of $12 for all standard sized orders around Australia with a total order value of less than $130.\r\n\r\nAll orders totalling over $150.00 in value, will be sent as registered post for security purposes. It is the customer’s responsibility to ensure the correct delivery address is provided.\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly accepts direct debit and the following credit cards: American Express, Visa and MasterCard.\r\n\r\n<b>Returns</b>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Process</span></b>\r\n\r\nYour complete satisfaction is our top priority! If you are not 100% satisfied with your purchase, your goods can be returned for an exchange or refund.\r\n\r\nThe returned item must be new (not dirty, used or washed), in the same condition you received it, in the original packaging, and sellable. We reserve the right to refuse a claim that does not meet these requirements.\r\n\r\nDiscounted products cannot be refunded or exchanged.\r\n\r\nWhen returning a product, you must contact our customer care team within 7 days of receiving the product, so they can assist you with your exchange or refund. For a refund, we will ask you to provide us with a valid proof of purchase and copy of the online delivery note. This is to ensure we can process return credits to the original purchaser of the product.\r\n\r\nWe reserve the right to cancel your order if:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>We have insufficient stock to deliver the products you have ordered; or</li>\r\n	<li>We do not deliver to your area or State or Territory; or\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>If one or more of the products you ordered was listed with incorrect information for whatever reason including but not limited to price and/or description; or</li>\r\n	<li>If your payment was declined by your financial institution; or</li>\r\n	<li>You have not complied with our Terms and Conditions of Use.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Time</span></b>\r\n\r\nFor a refund, goods must be returned within 14 days from the date of delivery. Otherwise we will try to replace the product with a product of similar or equal value if the original product is not available. A replacement product will be dispatched within 2 business days from the date of receiving your returned product. Delivery will follow the details provided in our Delivery Policy.\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Payment</span></b>\r\n\r\nAny return shipment postage costs, including express post, cannot be refunded.\r\n\r\nRefunds can only be processed to the original purchaser of the item. All return credits and refunds are processed within approximately 7-10 days upon arrival of the returned item at our warehouse. Sweet Baby Lilly cannot be held responsible for any items undelivered by Australia Post.\r\n\r\n<b>Customer Care</b>\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly appreciates your visit and would like to assist you in any way possible. For any questions or concerns, please call our customer care team at 1300 66 10 72 or email at <a href=\"mailto:info@sweetbabylilly.com.au\">info@sweetbabylilly.com.au</a>\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly team", "Delivery and Return Information", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "124-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-06-06 05:05:23", "2014-06-06 05:05:23", "", "124", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/index.php/124-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
