by us to you. In no event shall we be liable for any claims or damages including, but not limited to, claims for faulty design, negligent or misleading advice, damages arising from loss or use of the products, and any indirect, special or consequential damages or injury to any person or entity.\r\n\r\nIf we become liable to you for loss or damage of any kind arising out of these Terms and Conditions, your use of the Site or in connection with the relationship established by it, our liability is reduced to the extent (if any) that you cause or contribute to the loss or damage. This applies whether our liability is in contract, tort (including negligence), under any law or otherwise.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Prices</b>\r\n\r\nAll prices quoted on our Site are in Australian dollars (AUD).  We endeavour to ensure that our price list is current and reserve the right to amend our prices at any time.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Payment Security</b>\r\n\r\nWe have taken every possible measure to ensure that you can purchase online with complete confidence.\r\n\r\nWe have a secure transaction system which uses 128 bit Secure Sockets Layer technology (SSL) to ensure your online shopping experience is safe and secure at all times.  SSL is the industry standard for encryption technology.\r\n\r\nIf you are concerned about using your credit/debit card online, you can contact us for more information or assistance.\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n<b>Use and Intellectual Property Rights</b>\r\n\r\nYou may use the Site and the information contained within it for your own personal and non-commercial use only.\r\n\r\nThe information and material contained within this Site (including images, illustrations, graphics, designs, photographs, icons, logos and written materials) are copyright, trademarks and other intellectual property owned or licensed by Sweet Baby Lilly. You may make any copies of any information reasonably incidental to your viewing of the Site and may retain a single permanent copy for your personal reference. The information may not otherwise be used, copied, reproduced, published, stored in a retrieval system, altered, transmitted in any form or by any means in whole or in part (except where by law such use cannot be prohibited) without our prior written approval.\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n<b>Product Information</b>\r\n\r\nProducts displayed on the Site may be available in selected stores throughout Australia.  In some cases, products displayed for sale on the Site may not be available in all stores.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Design Protection</b>\r\n\r\nNo rights in the design of our products, or designs incorporated in our products, will pass to you because of your purchase of our products.  You agree not to copy or reproduce, or cause to be copied or reproduced, either directly or indirectly, our products, product designs, designs incorporated in our products, or product packaging.  This provision will survive termination of these Terms and Conditions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Colours</b>\r\n\r\nWe have made every effort to display the colours of our products that appear on the Site as accurately as possible.  Because the actual colours you see will depend on your monitor, we cannot guarantee that your monitor’s display of any colour will be accurate.\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n<b>Force Majeure</b>\r\n\r\nIf by reason of any fact, circumstance, matter or thing beyond our reasonable control we are unable to perform in whole or in part any obligation to you we are relieved of that obligation to the extent and for the period that we are so unable to perform and we are not liable to you in respect of such inability.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>External Websites and Third Party Trademarks</b>\r\n\r\nThis website may contain links to external websites that are not operated by us.  We make no representations or warranties about those external websites and have no responsibility or liability for them.  You agree that your access to, and use of, them is at your risk absolutely.\r\n\r\nThird party trademarks, trade names, product names and logos contained on the Site may be trademarks of their respective owners.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Severability</b>\r\n\r\nIf any provision of these Terms and Conditions is found to be void or unenforceable at law, that provision will not affect any other provision of these Terms and Conditions and, as far as is possible, will be read down to the extent required to make it enforceable.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Governing Law</b>\r\n\r\nThese Terms and Conditions are governed by the law in force in the State of New South Wales, Australia.", "Terms and Conditions of Use", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "120-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-06-06 05:07:07", "2014-06-06 05:07:07", "", "120", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/index.php/120-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
