INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("194", "2", "2014-06-15 05:42:55", "2014-06-15 05:42:55", "<b>Sweet Baby Lilly stands for safety, quality and style. We believe in providing only the best for you and your baby.</b>\r\n\r\nOur range of stylish and brightly coloured baby sleeping bags has been designed to provide a safe and healthy sleeping environment for your baby. Your peace of mind is our priority.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Certified to the highest children’s sleeping product safety standards: Australian AS/NZS 1249:2003, and American CPSIA.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">100% super soft cotton to prevent overheating.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Protective cotton layer around zipper to protect baby’s skin, and non-metal zipper pull to protect baby’s teeth.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Provides a stable sleeping environment for baby by supporting a consistent body temperature.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Non restrictive, unique bell-curved shape to stimulate baby’s hip movement.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Seamless lining for baby’s comfort.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe take pride in using only the finest quality cotton and lead-free materials, while maintaining strict quality control around fabric selection and product manufacturing to meet the quality demands of safety conscious mums.\r\n\r\nAdditional features such as oversized and reversed zippers for easy nappy changes, and two breathable cotton layers for ventilation, make Sweet Baby Lilly wearable baby blankets safe, snug and easy to use.\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly wearable baby blankets will help your baby sleep tight, so you both enjoy a well deserved rest, every night.\r\n\r\n<b>Sweet dreams!</b>\r\n\r\n<strong><b>Juliette (founder, Sweet Baby Lilly).</b></strong>", "Home", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "14-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-06-15 05:42:55", "2014-06-15 05:42:55", "", "14", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/14-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("199", "2", "2014-06-15 06:18:41", "2014-06-15 06:18:41", "<a href=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1.png\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-135\" alt=\"OurStory1\" src=\"http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OurStory1-253x300.png\" width=\"253\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSweet Baby Lilly, an international brand of safe, premium quality and stylish baby sleeping products, was founded by Juliette Tanamal after she gave birth to her beautiful daughter, Lilly-Ann in 2012.\r\n\r\nAs most new Moms do, Juliette extensively researched the different options of all things baby – including baby bedding and sleeping materials. The research she encountered indicate that baby sleeping bags, also known as wearable baby blankets, provided a safer and healthier alternative to loose sheets and blankets. Surprisingly, she experienced that many parents in Europe, Australia and the US were still using loose blankets to keep their babies snug. After trialing for herself, she also found that her precious Lilly-Ann improved her sleep patterns with the use of baby sleeping bags.\r\n\r\nAs a result, Juliette became an advocate for baby sleeping bags, however found it a struggle to find sleeping bags that were not only safe, but also of high quality and fashionable enough to suit her as a young new mom. The ones she did find were either overpriced, poorly made, didn’t meet safety standards or just simply too plain in design.\r\n\r\nIt was at this time that Juliette decided to make it her mission to create a range of baby sleeping products that were not only cute and stylish, but also met the highest quality and safety standards. Hence, Sweet Baby Lilly was born, giving parents peace of mind and moms and babies a well deserved rest.", "Our Story", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "18-revision-v1", "", "", "2014-06-15 06:18:41", "2014-06-15 06:18:41", "", "18", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/18-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
