INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("282", "2", "2015-05-03 11:56:09", "2015-05-03 11:56:09", "The Sweet Baby Lilly Hot Pink sleeping bag is a safe, stylish and adorable baby sleeping bag for the hip, modern mum. The 100% super soft cotton sleeping bag with cheerful, bright dotted design and cute decorative white band will surely make mum and baby smile.\n\nWith safety features like zipper protection layers, wide armholes for ventilation, and a teeth-safe zipper pull tab, this baby sleeping bag is a must-have for safety conscious mums who demand the highest in quality.\n\nThe super soft wearable baby blanket is made with 2 layers of breathable premium cotton. It has a non restrictive bell-curved shape to stimulate leg and hip movement, a soft flat seamless cotton lining for additional comfort, and an oversized side zipper making nappy changes a breeze.\n\nThe Sweet Baby Lilly Hot Pink baby sleeping bag meets the highest Australian and American Product Safety Standards, so you and your baby can enjoy a well deserved rest every night.\n<h2>Product Features</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Certified for Australian AS/NZS 1249:2003 and American CPSIA Safety Standards.</li>\n	<li>Oversized side zipper for smooth nappy changes.</li>\n	<li>2 breathable layers made from 100% premium cotton to prevent overheating.</li>\n	<li>Protective cotton layer on the inside of the zipper to protect baby’s skin against zipper teeth.</li>\n	<li>Firm pearl-coloured shoulder snaps making it easy to dress baby even when they sleep.</li>\n	<li>Flat, seamless, cosy and comfortable lining that feels like a blanket.</li>\n	<li>Non restrictive bell-curved design to support leg and hip movement.</li>\n	<li>Machine washable and can be tumble dried on low heat.</li>\n	<li>Available in sizes 0-6 mths, 6-18 mths and 18-36 mths.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Material</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>100% premium soft cotton.</li>\n	<li>Non-metal and lead-free zipper and shoulder snaps.</li>\n</ul>", "Hot Pink", "<ul>\n	<li>Firm stylish pearl-coloured shoulder snaps for easy wearing.</li>\n	<li>Protective cotton lining to protect baby skin from zipper.</li>\n	<li>Flat, seamless lining for comfort and safety.</li>\n	<li>Oversized reversed zipper for easy nappy changes.</li>\n	<li>Non restrictive wide bell-curved design to stimulate leg movement.</li>\n</ul>", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "60-autosave-v1", "", "", "2015-05-03 11:56:09", "2015-05-03 11:56:09", "", "60", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/60-autosave-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("284", "1", "2015-05-07 13:12:52", "2015-05-07 13:12:52", "<b>Baby sleeping bags designed by Sweet Baby Lilly stand for safety, quality and style. We believe in providing only<em> the best baby sleeping bags</em> for you and your baby.</b>\n\nOur range of <em>European </em>designed, <em>stylish</em> and <em>brightly coloured</em> baby sleeping bags have been specifically designed to provide a safe and healthy sleeping environment for your baby. Your baby or toddler might be alone in their baby sleeping bag for up to 12 hours at night so it needs to be as safe as possible. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Your peace of mind is our priority</span>.\n\n<strong>Baby sleeping bag safety features</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Certified to the highest children’s sleeping product <strong>safety standards: Australian</strong> AS/NZS 1249:2003, and <strong>American</strong> CPSIA.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>100% breathable cotton</strong> for ventilation to prevent overheating.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Protective</strong> cotton layer around <strong>zipper</strong> to protect baby’s skin against zipper teeth.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Closed </strong>and<strong> non-metal zipper pull </strong>to protect baby\'s teeth when pulling up their legs and suck on the zipper</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Provides a stable sleeping environment for baby by supporting a <strong>consistent body temperature</strong>.</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Non restrictive, unique bell-curved shape to <strong>stimulate baby’s hip development</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\nWe take pride in using only the <em>finest quality</em> cotton and<em> lead-free</em> materials, while maintaining strict quality control around fabric selection and product manufacturing to meet the quality demands of safety conscious mums.\n\n<strong>Additional baby sleeping bag features</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Non-stretch premium cotton to avoid stretching of neck holes and stepping out of the bag.</li>\n	<li>Oversized and reversed zippers for <strong>easy nappy changes.</strong></li>\n	<li>Super soft and seamless cotton inner lining for baby’s<strong> comfort.</strong></li>\n	<li>Size specific and <strong>fitted neck hole</strong> to avoid slipping into the baby sleeping bag.</li>\n	<li>Size specific and <strong>fitted arm hole</strong> for ventilation to prevent overheating.</li>\n	<li><strong>Front zipper</strong> to remember the parent to put the baby on the back to sleep safety.</li>\n</ul>\nAll these features will make Sweet Baby Lilly wearable baby sleeping bags <em>safe</em>, <em>cosy</em> and <em>easy to use</em>. Sweet Baby Lilly baby sleeping bags will help your baby sleep tight, so you both enjoy a well deserved rest, every night.\n\n<b>Sweet dreams!</b>\n\n<strong><b>Juliette (founder, Sweet Baby Lilly).</b></strong>", "Home", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "14-autosave-v1", "", "", "2015-05-07 13:12:52", "2015-05-07 13:12:52", "", "14", "http://sweetbabylilly.com.au/14-autosave-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
